        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nCurious to know what the YAML parsing issue is and how it applies to OOM?  Helm doesn't seem to have any troubles processing the templates with the mixed notation although I agree being consistent is a good thing!\nAlso this Jira Issue is tagged to the Beijing release.  Does this need to be done now?",
