        "timestamp": "2017-10-27 06:54:38.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(2 comments)\n\nCurious to know what the YAML parsing issue is and how it applies to OOM?\n\nwe tried to add volume mounts dynamically in the yaml for a CI/CD setup because some onap components have not externalized their configuration. for e.g. configuration of sdnc adaptor in mso.\nwe have raised a bug on the components and most likely in future releases all configuration will be externalized.\nThe parsing fails because of the absence of quotes and we feel it is better to be consistent.",
        "patchset_number": 2
